6
00:00:19,760 --> 00:00:22,160
<i>Strah nas drzao daleko od njih.</i>

7
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:27,080
<i>Dugo nakon sto su pale bombe...</i>

8
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:30,120
<i>nakon sto su kuga i zaraza
odradile svoje...</i>

9
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:34,440
<i>Mi, nekolicina prezivelih,
zivimo u strahu</i>

10
00:00:34,720 --> 00:00:36,360
<i>i bez nade.</i>

11
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:40,200
<i>Ali ovo je novo mesto...</i>

12
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:42,880
<i>Novo vreme.</i>

13
